---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Refund Policy" description="Refund Policy for digital karaoke tracks.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="bg-indigo-900/30 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl relative">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">Refund Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-pink max-w-none text-purple-100 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          At HolyfireMedia, customer satisfaction is a priority. Please review our policy regarding digital downloads and refunds.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Digital Products</h2>
        <p>
          Because our products are digital audio files (MP3/WAV) that are instantly delivered upon purchase, we generally do not offer refunds once the download link has been provided and accessed.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Exceptions</h2>
        <p>
          Refunds may be granted under the following exceptional circumstances:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 marker:text-pink-500">
          <li>The downloaded file is corrupted or unplayable, and our technical support cannot resolve the issue.</li>
          <li>Duplicate accidental purchases of the exact same track within a 24-hour window.</li>
          <li>The wrong track was delivered by our system compared to what was shown in the receipt.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Requesting a Refund</h2>
        <p>
          To request a refund, please contact us within 7 days of your purchase detailing the issue. 
          <br>Email: <a href="mailto:jmmusicdistribution@gmail.com" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300 font-bold mt-2 inline-block">jmmusicdistribution@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
